title: Guide to Digital Home Technology Integration
description:
Quentin Wells, "Guide to Digital Home Technology Integration"
English | 2008 | ISBN: 1435400623 | 544 pages | PDF | 10,1 MB

The most complete, up-to-date resource for home technology integration and home automation available, Residential Integrator's Guide to Digital Home Technology Integration explores how the latest high-tech systems converge to create integrated, whole-home unified systems.

With a focus on installation, troubleshooting, and maintenance, coverage includes LANs, internet connectivity, video and audio systems, telephone systems, security systems, lighting controls, and more.
